main event: A star-shaped object was observed in Stockton, California on September 13, 1956, heading north at a very high rate of speed.
interesting points: The object was about 1/50 the diameter of the sun,The sighting was made from an aircraft at approximately 9,000 ft,The object blinked out of sight for one minute,The sighting was reported by the captain of United Airlines Flight # 255,The report was classified as top secret.
